criteria.textblock:
        The inclusion criteria will be:

          1. patients with clinical signs and symptoms of COVID-19; and

          2. patients over 18 years and below 60 years of age.

        The exclusion criteria will be:

          1. participate in another clinical intervention study;

          2. you have a disease or other medical condition that prevents you from using the
             medications for this intervention;

          3. patient incapable of ingesting, retaining and absorbing the intervention medications;
             and (d) is mentally disabled.
